<h1>Waste Reduction Tips</h1>

<p>Follow these tips to reduce waste and improve your recycling habits:</p>

<ul>
    <li>**Reduce**: Buy products with less packaging and in bulk to reduce waste.</li>
    <li>**Reuse**: Use reusable bags, bottles, and containers instead of single-use items.</li>
    <li>**Recycle**: Separate recyclables like paper, cardboard, plastics, and metals.</li>
    <li>**Compost**: Compost organic waste like food scraps and yard waste.</li>
    <li>**Repair**: Fix broken items instead of throwing them away.</li>
    <li>**Donate**: Give away items you no longer need to charity or someone who can use them.</li>
</ul>

